#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat <<'EOF'
AI terminal shortcuts

Zellij navigation
  Alt+h / Alt+l        focus left / right pane
  Alt+j / Alt+k        focus down / up pane
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+t 1      go to Agents tab
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+t 2      go to ops tab
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+t 3      go to llm tab
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+t 4      go to sec tab
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+t 5      go to help tab

Zellij panes
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+p f      fullscreen focused pane, repeat to restore
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+p x      close focused pane
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+p r      new pane to the right
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+p d      new pane below
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+p c      rename focused pane

Zellij resize
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+n        resize mode
  h / j / k / l        resize focused pane
  + / -                grow / shrink
  Esc or Enter         exit resize mode

Zellij scroll and search
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+s        scroll mode
  j / k                scroll line
  Ctrl+f / Ctrl+b      page down / page up
  s                    search in scrollback
  Ctrl+c               return to bottom

Zellij session
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+o d      detach session, keeps agents running
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+o w      session manager
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+o l      layout manager
  Alt+F4 / window X    quit the visible Zellij session

LLM monitoring
  /home/bz/bin/bzserv-llm-monitor gpu
  /home/bz/bin/bzserv-llm-monitor status
  /home/bz/bin/bzserv-llm-monitor traffic
  /home/bz/bin/bzserv-llm-monitor webui-logs
  /home/bz/bin/bzserv-llm-monitor ollama-logs

Security monitoring
  /home/bz/bin/bzserv-security-monitor overview
  /home/bz/bin/bzserv-security-monitor surface
  /home/bz/bin/bzserv-security-monitor auth
  /home/bz/bin/bzserv-security-monitor firewall

Reload visible terminal config
  terminal-theme light       sync config and apply light colors
  terminal-theme auto        sync config and pick theme by time
  terminal-ai                from a normal shell outside Zellij
  TERMINAL_AI_REFRESH=always terminal-ai
  wezterm &

Existing sessions
  The Alt+F4 quit behavior applies to newly started sessions.
  For an old ai session, run once:
  zellij kill-session ai
  terminal-ai

Close one session from shell
  zellij list-sessions
  zellij kill-session ai
  zellij kill-session main

Detach without killing
  Ctrl+g Ctrl+o d            detach from inside Zellij
  zellij attach ai           return later

WezTerm
  Ctrl+Shift+F9        open maximized AI cockpit
  Ctrl+Shift+F10       open maximized Codex-only session
  Ctrl+Shift+F11       open maximized Claude-only session
  Ctrl+Shift+F         search terminal output
  Ctrl+Shift+PageUp    scroll page up
  Ctrl+Shift+PageDown  scroll page down
  Alt+Shift+V          paste latest screenshot path

Theme switching
  Run terminal-theme from a normal shell pane.
  Restart Codex if its input box keeps old cached colors.

Daily flow
  1. Use Alt+h/j/k/l to move without mouse.
  2. Use Ctrl+g Ctrl+p f for full-screen Codex/Claude.
  3. Use Ctrl+g Ctrl+t 1/2/3/4/5 to jump tabs.
  4. Use Ctrl+g Ctrl+o d before closing WezTerm.
EOF
